title: True Food Kitchen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Located at Fashion Island and is frequented by tourists and shoppers. Menu is centered on the principals of Dr. Andrew Weil's Anti-Inflammatory Diet & Food Pyramid, with several ovo/lacto vegetarian dishes and a few vegan ones, marked. Spacious, sleek, simple, and modern.
